		<description><![CDATA[custom_terminal git clone git@github.com:logmancuso/custom_terminal.git add this to the end of .bashrc in the $HOME dir for f in $HOME/.custom_terminal/*; do if [ ${f: -3} == ".sh" ] then . $f fi done then run exec bash]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1>custom_terminal</h1>
<p>git clone git@github.com:logmancuso/custom_terminal.git</p>
<p>add this to the end of .bashrc in the $HOME dir</p>
<pre><code class="">for f in $HOME/.custom_terminal/*; do
   if [ ${f: -3} == ".sh" ]
   then
        . $f
   fi
done

</code></pre>
<p>then run exec bash</p>
]]></content:encoded>
